Boca_Raton.Florida Atlantic University Library:
The Florida Atlantic University Libraries comprises a main library at the Boca Raton Campus, the College Library at the Davie, campus, the Broward County Main Library, the FAU Harbor Branch Library, the John D. MacArthur Campus Library, and the St. Lucie West Library at the Fort Pierce campus.


== S.E. Wimberly Library ==
The S.E. Wimberly Library, located on the main campus in Boca Raton, is FAU's main library.
